### 4.4 [templates/index.html](file:///d:/MLDL/DL/chat_with_pdf/templates/index.html) — The Chat Interface

A single-page application with **inline CSS + JavaScript** (plus an external CSS file). Major sections:

#### HTML Structure
| Section | Element ID | Purpose |
|---|---|---|
| **Sidebar** | `#sidebar` | Contains logo, upload zone, file info, and footer |
| **Upload Zone** | `#uploadZone` | Drag-and-drop area for PDF files |
| **File Info** | `#fileInfo` | Shows uploaded filename + chunk count |
| **Progress Bar** | `#uploadProgress` | Shows upload/processing progress |
| **Chat Header** | — | Title + status badge (shows if PDF is loaded) |
| **Messages Container** | `#messagesContainer` | Where chat messages appear |
| **Welcome Screen** | `#welcomeScreen` | Shown before any messages, with feature cards |
| **Input Bar** | — | Text area + send button for asking questions |

#### JavaScript Logic

**PDF Upload Flow:**
1. User clicks upload zone or drags a PDF → triggers [handleUpload(file)](file:///d:/MLDL/DL/chat_with_pdf/templates/index.html#900-947)
2. Shows progress bar with animated stages
3. Sends the file to `/upload` via `fetch()` with `FormData`
4. On success: shows file card, enables chat input, updates status badge to green
5. On error: shows error message in chat

**Chat Flow:**
1. User types a question + presses Enter (or clicks Send) → triggers [sendQuestion()](file:///d:/MLDL/DL/chat_with_pdf/templates/index.html#962-991)
2. User's message appears in chat (purple bubble, right-aligned)
3. Typing indicator appears (3 animated dots)
4. Sends question to `/ask` via `fetch()` with JSON body
5. On response: removes typing indicator, shows AI answer (dark bubble, left-aligned)
6. On error: shows red error message

**Key Functions:**
| Function | Purpose |
|---|---|
| [handleUpload(file)](file:///d:/MLDL/DL/chat_with_pdf/templates/index.html#900-947) | Validates PDF, uploads to server, updates UI |
| [sendQuestion()](file:///d:/MLDL/DL/chat_with_pdf/templates/index.html#962-991) | Sends question to `/ask`, handles response |
| [addMessage(role, text)](file:///d:/MLDL/DL/chat_with_pdf/templates/index.html#992-1012) | Creates a chat bubble (user/assistant/system) |
| [addTypingIndicator()](file:///d:/MLDL/DL/chat_with_pdf/templates/index.html#1013-1033) | Shows "AI is thinking..." animation |
| [removeTypingIndicator(id)](file:///d:/MLDL/DL/chat_with_pdf/templates/index.html#1034-1038) | Removes the typing animation |

#### UI Design Features
- **Dark premium theme** with purple/indigo accent colors
- **Glassmorphism** (blurred, semi-transparent backgrounds)
- **Animated gradient blobs** in the background
- **Smooth animations** on messages, uploads, and hover states
- **Responsive design** — works on mobile with a slide-out sidebar

